Name: Create New Blog Entry

Ojective: Verify that a new entry can be added to the blog by a user

Enviroment: 
    * Google Chrome Version 102.0.5005.115
    * OSX version 10.15.7

Preconditions:
    * Enter to The Blog Webpage
    * Must be logged into any user

Steps:
    1. Open the webpage
    2. Click on "Add new post"
    3. Type a Title
    4. Type a slug for direction
    5. Upload a cover art
    6. Select the satus as "Publish"
    7. Type the blog content
    8. Click Save

Expected Result:
    * The new post must be created, and can be seeing under "Blog" page, with username, date created, title and short info of the blog content.
